title: #92Noon! Boudreau/Lee/Leber/Korzo/Norv
description: Bruce Boudreau, starts the show! Then memories/stories on the life of Chris Doleman with his former long-time Vikings teammate Carl Lee, Leber in studio during the 10a hour, Korzo starts the final hour, then Uncle NORVVVV! finishes things off with a covenant catch-up!
